  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0bae\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb9\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb7\u0ba3 \u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9c\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bbe",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New President should release Ranjan Ramanayake - Harshana Rajakaruna",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Harshana Rajakaruna, Member of Parliament of United People's Shakti said that the first duty of the new president is to demand the release of Ranjan Ramanayaka.",
        "On Tuesday 12th, members of United People's Power visited former Member of Parliament Ranjan Ramanayaka, who is currently serving his prison sentence in Welikada Prison, Colombo. He said this while commenting to the media.",
        "It has been a year and a half since Ranjan Ramanayake was imprisoned. He went to jail by telling the truth.",
        "We had told the President several times to release him. However, President Gotabaya Rajapakash did not take any action in this regard.",
        "But in the Rajapaksh government, murderers and drug smugglers have been freed in the amnesty.",
        "Former Member of Parliament Ranjan Ramanayake was not jailed for murder or drug trafficking.",
        "He is always telling the truth openly. That is why he has this condition. So after the resignation of Gotabaya Rajapaksh, a new president will be elected.",
        "He said that the first duty of the newly elected president is to release the demand for the release of Ranjan Ramanayake."
      ],
